Kou2-cha2 kou2-cha2, ti7 chit8 e5 hiuN-sia7, u7 chit8 e5 lau7 a2-po5, i u7 chhi7 3 chiah ti-a2-kiaN2.  Chong2-si7 lau7 a-po5 in-ui7 san3, bo5 mih8 thang hou7 in chiah8, sou2-i2 pang3 in ti7 goa7-bin7, ng3-bang7 in oe7 ka-ki7 khi3 chhe7 tioh8 ho2 e5 chiah8-mih8.  Chit 3 chiah ti-a2-kiaN2 kap in e5 chu2-lang5 li7-khui liau2-au7, chiu7 long2 chhut-khi3.  
