Soe3 chiah ti-a2-kiaN2 eng7 kiaN-hiaN5 e5 sim in3 kong2, “Oh!  Chin...chin ho2 chiah8, goa2 tim3 chit8 liap8 hou7 li2 houN3?”  Kong2 liau2 tui3 chhiu7-teng2 tim3 chit8 liap8 hou7 hou5-li5, i tiau5-kou3-i3 tim3 ti7 soaN-phiaN5, hou7 phong7-ko2 lin3 tui3 soaN-kha loh8-khi3, tng hou5-li5 chau2 khi3 khioh e5 si5, i koaN2-kin2 peh loh8-lai5, chau2 tng2-khi3 chhu3-nih.  
Hou5-li5 khioh tioh8 phong7-ko2 koh to3-tng2 lai5 e5 si5, khoaN3-kiN3 chhiu7-teng2 e5 soe3 chiah ti-a2-kiaN2 i2-keng chau2 tng2-khi3, hui-siong5 e5 siu7-khi3.  Sou2-i2 i koat-sim beh chiah8 hit chiah ti-a2-kiaN2, i chau2 khi3 soe3 chiah ti-a2-kiaN2 e5 chhu3, ka7 ti-a2-kiaN2 kong2, “Goa2 beh tui3 ian-tang5 liu loh8-khi3 li2 e5 chhu3 beh chiah8 li2.”  
